         Hash Cond: (cst_int2.a = cst_int8.a)
         ->  Seq Scan on cst_int2  (cost=0.00..375.00 rows=34100 width=2)
         ->  Hash  (cost=321.00..321.00 rows=28700 width=8)
               ->  Seq Scan on cst_int8  (cost=0.00..321.00 rows=28700 width=8)
